<item>
            <title>[GROOVY-6741] Generic Traits and SAM type coercion</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/GROOVY-6741</link>
                <project id="12318123" key="GROOVY">Groovy</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The following code:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;trait GPredicate&amp;lt;T&amp;gt; {
    &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;abstract&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;code-object&quot;&gt;boolean&lt;/span&gt; test( T t )
}

GPredicate&amp;lt;&lt;span class=&quot;code-object&quot;&gt;Integer&lt;/span&gt;&amp;gt; p = { &lt;span class=&quot;code-object&quot;&gt;Integer&lt;/span&gt; n -&amp;gt; n &amp;gt; 1 }
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Results in an exception:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;A transform used a generics containing ClassNode GPredicate &amp;lt;T &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;extends&lt;/span&gt; java.lang.&lt;span class=&quot;code-object&quot;&gt;Object&lt;/span&gt; -&amp;gt; java.lang.&lt;span class=&quot;code-object&quot;&gt;Object&lt;/span&gt;&amp;gt; &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;for&lt;/span&gt; the &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;super&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;class &lt;/span&gt;GPredicate$TraitAdapter directly. You are not supposed to &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;do&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;this&lt;/span&gt;. Please create a &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;new&lt;/span&gt; ClassNode referring to the old ClassNode and use the &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;new&lt;/span&gt; ClassNode instead of the old one. Otherwise the compiler will create wrong descriptors and a potential NullPointerException in TypeResolver in the OpenJDK. If &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;this&lt;/span&gt; is not your own doing, please report &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;this&lt;/span&gt; bug to the writer of the transform.
 at line: -1, column: -1
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description>
